{"tid":804633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國研究指一年少於3周假期會早死","createTime":"2018-09-03T07:10:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T10:39:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e6468ffe38a7f5fe73ff8073a0d5b86f6b99b960","tid":804633,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"香港人假期vs芬蘭人假期<br />\n<br />\n外國有研究發現，人的壽命與一年獲得的假期有莫大關係。如果一年内放假少於3周，壽命會較其他人短，而這也與長時間工作、睡眠時間少有關。<br />\n<br />\n這項研究於1974至1975年進行，研究了1222名任職企業行政人員的中年男性，他們都有最少一項心血管疾病的高危因素，如過重、吸煙、高血壓或高膽固醇等。研究為612名測試者每4個月提供醫學咨詢，建議他們做運動、要有健康飲食等，同時獲處方降血壓藥。另一組測試者則沒有特別醫療照顧，只提供一般醫療服務。<br />\n<br />\n最近，芬蘭赫爾辛基大學醫學院教授斯特蘭德貝里的團隊，追蹤當年研究的測試者情況，發現在1974至2004年間，一年放假少於3周的人，死亡風險較放假多過3周的人高37%。報告認為，放假少、睡眠少而工作多形成了壓力，為生活方式帶來影響，遠超醫療服務能帶來的好處。即使有健康的生活方式，也不能彌補工作辛苦和沒假期帶來的負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n網民秒回：「香港人好長命」、「香港：一年放假多於三日易窮死」，亦指香港情況有異：「港人工時長，假期少，有利長壽。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upower.com.hk/article/264478-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E6%96%BC3%E5%91%A8%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%97%A9%E6%AD%BB-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A7%92%E5%9B%9Eko%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upower.com.hk%2Farticle%2F264478-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B0%2591%25E6%2596%25BC3%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2581%2587%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%25AD%25BB-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25A7%2592%25E5%259B%259Eko%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599&d=2udh5xhCYt10QHcWxQFnEwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b3fc7ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.upower.com.hk/article/264478-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E6%96%BC3%E5%91%A8%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%97%A9%E6%AD%BB-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A7%92%E5%9B%9Eko%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99</a>"},{"pid":"d91c430ddcdeef4c9118f17dc43c436992dd4876","tid":804633,"uid":161341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:21:47.000Z","msg":"要返工，死亡？不了"},{"pid":"11b58697bc81f40bd2a5067d360096fa3be94f7f","tid":804633,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:24:22.000Z","msg":"跟住又有人會話香港人短命d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大佬 短命既多數絕症死<br />\n死得好痛苦好慘果隻<br />\n舒舒服服長命活到自然死最爽"},{"pid":"787d60602eff93d15709a835705e2b0207fc363a","tid":804633,"uid":65984,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:42:56.000Z","msg":"試解釋香港工時全球領先, 但人均壽命全球最高<br />\n<br />\n專家食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dae56cea0d8bc61591570ea2444072d0455378","tid":804633,"uid":201403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:43:57.000Z","msg":"一年少於三週假期 話唔定早死係幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df74e298a09578de010197300dfed5c372f03e2","tid":804633,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:44:27.000Z","msg":"腦細：星期日有得你放過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fba70260426bef492367b3c55e23423558058b9","tid":804633,"uid":11261,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"香港人有撚三周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣全世界最長命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f55e9149964472ff9d8b9686cf40aebea5ba991","tid":804633,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:47:09.000Z","msg":"事實證明專家都係呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7011402c9f03f3dfbb714331bb5ac8e71383e8","tid":804633,"uid":194609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:47:33.000Z","msg":"美國研究指呼吸多於100年會高機率死亡"},{"pid":"5f54c7f3d2cb3ad6e87846815c595c0f5d0eb8e9","tid":804633,"